snippet.title: Mahindra Thar Roxx 5-Door Walkaround | Gagan Choudhary
snippet.description:

snippet.title: Vande Mataram - A.R. Rahman| Maa Tujhe Salaam| Independence Day Song
snippet.description:
Celebrate 78th Independence Day and immerse yourself in the soul-stirring sounds of "Vande Mataram" as A.R. Rahman brings to life the spirit of India with his timeless anthem, "Maa Tujhe Salaam." Penned by Mehboob and composed by the maestro himself, this song has become a symbol of national pride and unity.

Song Name – Maa Tujhe Salaam 
Music – A.R. Rahman
Lyrics – Mehboob Kotwal
Producer & Director – Bharat Bala 

#maatujhesalaam #vandemataram #arrahman #independenceday #independencedayspecial

snippet.title: Mahindra Thar Roxx 5 door - Every Detail | AutoYogi | ICN Studio
snippet.description: Mahindra Thar’s 5-door version - Roxx - was finally launched in India on the evening of India’s 77th Independence Day. Similar to the 3-door version, it’s based on the same Scorpio N platform but several changes has been made to it to accommodate an extra row of seats and a bigger boot. The vehicle’s cabin too has seen an overhaul as it receives a revised dashboard layout that now accommodates a new 10.25-inch touchscreen, a 10.25-inch instrument cluster screen, soft touch material on top of the dash, a 360 degree camera, ventilated seats, electrically-adjustable driver seat, auto-dimming IRVM, panaromic sunroof, harmon-kardon music system, wireless charger, wireless apple carplay and android auto among others. So far we only know the prices of its base variants, the petrol base costs Rs 12.99 lakh (ex-showroom) and the diesel base costs Rs 13.99 lakh (ex-showroom). More details on its performance will be updated on 17th August. Stay tuned for that.

snippet.title: HIGHLIGHTS | Real Madrid 2-0 Atalanta | UEFA Super Cup 2024
snippet.description:
Watch the goals and highlights as Real Madrid became UEFA Super Cup 2024 champions after defeating Atalanta 2-0 in Warsaw (Real Madrid 2-0 Atalanta). Real Madrid have picked up their first piece of silverware of the 2024/25 season thanks to second half goals from Fede Valverde and new signing Kylian Mbappé. Valverde and Mbappé were assisted by Vini Jr. and Jude Bellingham respectively. With this victory, club captain Luka Modrić became the most decorated player in Real Madrid's history with 27 titles.
#6SuperCups

snippet.title: ₹12.99 lakhs Mahindra Thar Roxx 5-Door SUV Walkaround in Tamil: Interiors, Exteriors & More!
snippet.description:
The new Mahindra Thar Roxx 5-Door has finally arrived, and we're here to give you a comprehensive walkaround! Join us as we explore this highly anticipated SUV's interiors, exteriors, and all the key features.

Starting prices are ₹12.99 lakh for the Petrol MT RWD, which offers 162 hp and 330 Nm of torque, and ₹13.99 lakh for the Diesel MT RWD, which provides 152 hp and 330 Nm of torque. This model has 6 airbags, ESC, and 3-point seatbelts across all variants. Additional features include a 10.24-inch touchscreen infotainment system, 18-inch steel wheels, brake locking differential, driver’s seat height adjustment, LED projector headlamps and taillamps, push-button start, and rear AC vents.

Got questions about the Thar Roxx? Drop them in the comments, and don't forget to like and subscribe for more detailed reviews and updates!

Starting prices are ₹12.99 lakh for the Petrol MT RWD, which offers 162 hp and 330 Nm of torque, and ₹13.99 lakh for the Diesel MT RWD, which provides 152 hp and 330 Nm of torque. This model has 6 airbags, ESC, and 3-point seatbelts across all variants. Additional features include a 10.24-inch touchscreen infotainment system, 18-inch steel wheels, brake locking differential, driver’s seat height adjustment, LED projector headlamps and taillamps, push-button start, and rear AC vents.

Got questions about the Thar Roxx? Drop them in the comments, and don't forget to like and subscribe for more detailed reviews and updates!

In this video, we delve into the box office collections of some of the recent blockbuster movies in Bollywood and South Indian cinema.

Khel Khel mein 1st Day Box office collection,
Akshay Kumar's Comedy Drama entertainer "Khel Khel mein," Direct by Mudassar Aziz. the film has been creating waves at the box office with its high-octane action sequences and gripping storyline. ans Great Cast Including Ammy Virk Pragya Jaiswal Fardeen Khan Vaani Kapoor. The film has garnered impressive numbers at the box office, cementing Akshay Kumar's position as one of the top actors in the industry. Fans and critics alike have praised his performance in the movie, leading to a stellar box office collection. Khel Khel mein Movie Review & Khel Khel Mein Public review Coming Up,

Vedaa  Box office collection Day 1,
John Abraham starrer "Vedaa,"  Directed By Nikhil Advani a thrilling crime drama that has been a hit among audiences. John Abraham & Sharvari intense portrayal of his character has resonated with viewers, resulting in a strong box office performance for the film. "Vedaa" has proven to be a commercial success, showcasing John Abraham's star power and acting prowess. 
Vedaa Public Review & Veda Movie Review Out Soon,


Stree 2 movie Box office collection,
Shraddha Kapoor's horror-comedy "Stree 2," Directed By Amar Kaushik the film has been a favorite among audiences for its unique blend of humor and scares. Shraddha Kapoor's Pankaj Tripathi Rajkumar Rao stellar performance coupled with a captivating storyline has propelled "Stree 2" to great heights at the box office. The film's box office collection reflects the audience's love for this genre-bending film.
Stree 2 Movie Review & Stree 2 Public Review Coming Up,

Thanglaan Box office collection All Languages Worldwide,
Chiyaan Vikram's action thriller "Thanglaan," which has been making waves at the worldwide box office. Chiyaan Vikram's versatile acting and the film's gripping narrative have captured the audience's attention, leading to a strong box office performance globally. "Thanglaan" showcases Chiyaan Vikram's star power and acting chops, solidifying his position as a powerhouse performer in the industry.
Thangalaan Movie Hindi Review In Out Soon,

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Kaffara Episode 19 - [Eng Sub] - Ali Ansari - Laiba Khan - Zoya Nasir - 15th August 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Sitara, a lively orphan living with her brother, aunt, and uncle, finds joy in life's small things despite her aunt's poor treatment. Her aunt keeps her around because she has a share in the family's property.
Salar, the son of a wealthy businessman, is passionate about photography, which often earns him criticism from his family. With a pure heart, Salar is known for evading his responsibilities.
At her cousin's wedding, Sitara wrongly assumes Salar is the photographer. Salar develops a soft spot for Sitara after seeing how poorly she is treated. However, due to a conspiracy, objections arise about their closeness. Salar, once again, avoids the issue, leaving Sitara to face doubts from her own family.
Can Sitara prove she’s not guilty? Will Salar help her avoid further mistreatment? Will her family support Sitara? Can Salar show he genuinely cares? Will there be more plots against Sitara?

snippet.title: Rakesh Barot | Kajal Maheriya | રાકેશ બારોટ | કાજલ મહેરીયા | આઠમ આઈ ઢૂંકડી | Gujarati Love Song 2024
snippet.description:
મજા લો રાકેશ બારોટ અને કાજલ મહેરિયાના નવા સુપરહિટ ગુજરાતી લવ સોંગ "આથમ આવી ધુનકડી" માત્ર @SaregamaGujarati પર!

Enjoy Rakesh Barot and Kajal Maheriya's new superhit Gujarati Love song "Aatham Aai Dhunkadi" only on @SaregamaGujarati today!

Credits:
Singer: Rakesh Barot, Kajal Maheriya 
Producer: Red Velvet Cinema
Artist: Rakesh Barot, Kajal Maheriya, Neha Suthar, Lata Prajapati
Director: Jeet Vasava
Concept: Purvi Vasava
DOP: Dhruv Bhatiya
Asst. Director: Priyanka Chauhan
Choreographer: Deepak Turi
EditorI: Ravindra Rathod
Music: Mehul Barot, Rakesh Barot
Lyrics: Jigar Jesangpura,Jank Jesangpura
Jigar Jesangpura,Janak Jesangpura
Production: Jaydeep Chauhan (Sunny)
Creative Head: Dhyey Film Team & Manish Mehta
Technical support: Jenish Talaviya 
Art Setting: Rakesh Suthar, BabuSinh Thakor
Poster: Aman Agola
Light: Kalpesh jadav
Special Thanks: Dhaval Thakor,Dhaval Barot Shankar Thakor, Nilesh Joshi, 
Lal Bahi Nai, Sunil Cycle ( Kalol)
Recording: Dhoon Digital Recording Studio Adalaj


Lyrics:
હે ગોકુળ હે આઠમ
હે ગોકુળ આઠમ આઈ ઢૂંકડી રે
હે ઢોલા આઠમ આઈ ઢૂંકડી રે હે ભલે આઠમ આઈ વાલી ઢુંકડી
હે આયો મારા મૈયેર થી સંદેશ જાવું મારે પીયર વાળા દેશ
આઠમ આઈ સે પિયુ ઢૂંકડી રે
હે હમણાં જઈ આયા છો મૈયર હાચવો હમણાં આપડું ઘર
ખોટી વાતે મને ના ઓકડતી રે
હે આઠમ આઈ સે પિયુ ઢૂંકડી રે
હો ચમ ના પાડો પિયુ હૈયે હરખ સે
તમને ના કઉં તો બીજા કન જઈને કઇએ
હો બધી વાત હાચી પણ નોકરી સાત વાગે
તમારા જેમ ટિફિન કોણ કરી આપે
હે કરજો તમે બે દાડા કોક વેત આઇસ જલ્દી નહી કરું લેટ  
હે આઠમ આઈ સે ઢોલા ઢૂંકડી રે
નથી ભાવતું ઢોલા ભાવસે હે બારનું ભાવતું નથી ભોણું
ભૂખે રઉ કરું હુંતો એક ટોણું
ભલે આઠમ આઈ ઢુંકડી રે ,હે આઠમ આઈ સે પિયુ ઢૂંકડી રે
હો જવાદયોને મને જાજી રોકાઈ નઈ તોકણ
મને ખબર સે જાજા કોમ સે ઓયકણ
હો ઘરના કરો કોમ ખોટી મેલોદયો રાડ્યું
હવારથી એકની એક પકડી બેઠા વાતું
હે માં એ મને આપી જવાની રજા
તમે ના પાડસો તો આવશે નઈ મજા
છેલ્લી વખત કઉં છું જવાદયો રમવા રે..
રાજી થઈને હા હા રે ઢોલા
હે રાજી થઈને જો કોનુંડો રમવા જટ તૈયાર થો આવું  મેલવા
પાસો આઇશ વાલી તને તેડવા રે
હે આઠમ આઈ સે પિયુ ઢૂંકડી રે
હે ગોકુળ આઠમ આઈ ઢૂંકડી રે

#kajalmaheriya 
#saregamagujarati 
#rakeshbarotbestgujaratistaus

en.title: Rakesh Barot | Kajal Maheriya | રાકેશ બારોટ | કાજલ મહેરીયા | આઠમ આઈ ઢૂંકડી | Gujarati Love Song 2024
en.description:
મજા લો રાકેશ બારોટ અને કાજલ મહેરિયાના નવા સુપરહિટ ગુજરાતી લવ સોંગ "આથમ આવી ધુનકડી" માત્ર @SaregamaGujarati પર!

Enjoy Rakesh Barot and Kajal Maheriya's new superhit Gujarati Love song "Aatham Aai Dhunkadi" only on @SaregamaGujarati today!

Credits:
Singer: Rakesh Barot, Kajal Maheriya 
Producer: Red Velvet Cinema
Artist: Rakesh Barot, Kajal Maheriya, Neha Suthar, Lata Prajapati
Director: Jeet Vasava
Concept: Purvi Vasava
DOP: Dhruv Bhatiya
Asst. Director: Priyanka Chauhan
Choreographer: Deepak Turi
EditorI: Ravindra Rathod
Music: Mehul Barot, Rakesh Barot
Lyrics: Jigar Jesangpura,Jank Jesangpura
Jigar Jesangpura,Janak Jesangpura
Production: Jaydeep Chauhan (Sunny)
Creative Head: Dhyey Film Team & Manish Mehta
Technical support: Jenish Talaviya 
Art Setting: Rakesh Suthar, BabuSinh Thakor
Poster: Aman Agola
Light: Kalpesh jadav
Special Thanks: Dhaval Thakor,Dhaval Barot Shankar Thakor, Nilesh Joshi, 
Lal Bahi Nai, Sunil Cycle ( Kalol)
Recording: Dhoon Digital Recording Studio Adalaj


Lyrics:
હે ગોકુળ હે આઠમ
હે ગોકુળ આઠમ આઈ ઢૂંકડી રે
હે ઢોલા આઠમ આઈ ઢૂંકડી રે હે ભલે આઠમ આઈ વાલી ઢુંકડી
હે આયો મારા મૈયેર થી સંદેશ જાવું મારે પીયર વાળા દેશ
આઠમ આઈ સે પિયુ ઢૂંકડી રે
હે હમણાં જઈ આયા છો મૈયર હાચવો હમણાં આપડું ઘર
ખોટી વાતે મને ના ઓકડતી રે
હે આઠમ આઈ સે પિયુ ઢૂંકડી રે
હો ચમ ના પાડો પિયુ હૈયે હરખ સે
તમને ના કઉં તો બીજા કન જઈને કઇએ
હો બધી વાત હાચી પણ નોકરી સાત વાગે
તમારા જેમ ટિફિન કોણ કરી આપે
હે કરજો તમે બે દાડા કોક વેત આઇસ જલ્દી નહી કરું લેટ  
હે આઠમ આઈ સે ઢોલા ઢૂંકડી રે
નથી ભાવતું ઢોલા ભાવસે હે બારનું ભાવતું નથી ભોણું
ભૂખે રઉ કરું હુંતો એક ટોણું
ભલે આઠમ આઈ ઢુંકડી રે ,હે આઠમ આઈ સે પિયુ ઢૂંકડી રે
હો જવાદયોને મને જાજી રોકાઈ નઈ તોકણ
મને ખબર સે જાજા કોમ સે ઓયકણ
હો ઘરના કરો કોમ ખોટી મેલોદયો રાડ્યું
હવારથી એકની એક પકડી બેઠા વાતું
હે માં એ મને આપી જવાની રજા
તમે ના પાડસો તો આવશે નઈ મજા
છેલ્લી વખત કઉં છું જવાદયો રમવા રે..
રાજી થઈને હા હા રે ઢોલા
હે રાજી થઈને જો કોનુંડો રમવા જટ તૈયાર થો આવું  મેલવા
પાસો આઇશ વાલી તને તેડવા રે
હે આઠમ આઈ સે પિયુ ઢૂંકડી રે
હે ગોકુળ આઠમ આઈ ઢૂંકડી રે

snippet.title: Mufasa: The Lion King | Hindi Trailer | Shah Rukh Khan, Aryan Khan, AbRam Khan | In Cinemas Dec 20
snippet.description:
बस एक ही होगा जंगल का राजा 👑
The King Shah Rukh Khan is back as Mufasa 🦁 , with #AryanKhan and #AbRamKhan by his side
Mufasa: The Lion King in cinemas on 20th December, 2024

Exploring the unlikely rise of the beloved king of the Pride Lands, “Mufasa: The Lion King” enlists Rafiki to relay the legend of Mufasa to young lion cub Kiara, daughter of Simba and Nala, with Timon and Pumbaa lending their signature schtick. Told in flashbacks, the story introduces Mufasa as an orphaned cub, lost and alone until he meets a sympathetic lion named Taka—the heir to a royal bloodline. The chance meeting sets in motion an expansive journey of an extraordinary group of misfits searching for their destiny—their bonds will be tested as they work together to evade a threatening and deadly foe. 
 
Cast members that lent their voices to the film:
Shah Rukh Khan as Mufasa
Aryan Khan as Simba
AbRam Khan as Young Mufasa
Sanjay Mishra as Pumbaa
Shreyas Talpade as Timon
 
With an all-star roster of talent bringing new and fan-favorite characters to life, the film also has celebrated award-winning songwriter Lin-Manuel Miranda is writing the film’s songs produced by Mark Mancina and Miranda, with additional music and performances by Lebo M. 
 
Said Miranda, “Elton John. Tim Rice. Hans Zimmer. Lebo M. Mark Mancina. Beyoncé, Labrinth, Ilya Salmanzadeh. Beau Black, Ford Riley, the incredible music team on ‘The Lion Guard,’ and so many musical contributors over the years. ‘The Lion King’ has an incredible musical legacy with music from some of the greatest songwriters around, and I'm humbled and proud to be a part of it. It's been a joy working alongside Barry Jenkins to bring Mufasa's story to life, and we can't wait for audiences to experience this film in theaters."
 
Blending live-action filmmaking techniques with photoreal computer-generated imagery, “Mufasa: The Lion King” is directed by Barry Jenkins, produced by Adele Romanski & Mark Ceryak, and executive produced by Peter Tobyansen.

snippet.title: Google Pixel 9 Pro XL is pushing the limits... (Durability Test)
snippet.description:
Today we durability test the new Pixel 9 Pro XL. Get a screen protector before you need one: https://www.dbrand.com/pixel-9-series The google pixel 9 XL has quite possibly the worlds largest camera bump. Its not even a bump at this point - its a plateau. But... the rest of the flat glass design makes up for the giganticness of the camera units.  Plus... bigger cameras usually mean better pictures. But Ill let other reviewers handle the software side of new Pixel phones.  We are here to test the durability of the Pixel 9 pro XL to see if it can really handle 7 years worth of use. 

Get my teardown skin for your phone HERE: https://www.dbrand.com/teardown

----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Kaffara Episode 18 - [Eng Sub] - Ali Ansari - Laiba Khan - Zoya Nasir - 14th August 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Sitara, a lively orphan living with her brother, aunt, and uncle, finds joy in life's small things despite her aunt's poor treatment. Her aunt keeps her around because she has a share in the family's property.
Salar, the son of a wealthy businessman, is passionate about photography, which often earns him criticism from his family. With a pure heart, Salar is known for evading his responsibilities.
At her cousin's wedding, Sitara wrongly assumes Salar is the photographer. Salar develops a soft spot for Sitara after seeing how poorly she is treated. However, due to a conspiracy, objections arise about their closeness. Salar, once again, avoids the issue, leaving Sitara to face doubts from her own family.
Can Sitara prove she’s not guilty? Will Salar help her avoid further mistreatment? Will her family support Sitara? Can Salar show he genuinely cares? Will there be more plots against Sitara?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation 
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi 
Director: Muhammad Iftikhar Iffi
Writer: Shafia Khan

Cast :
Ali Ansari as Salar

snippet.title: पारंपरिक स्वादिष्ट व कुरकुरा घेवर,  घर पर ही बनाएं, आटे से | Malai Ghevar Recipe for Rakshabandhan
snippet.description:
घर पर बनाएं पारंपरिक स्वादिष्ट और कुरकुरा मलाई घेवर, आटे से, रक्षाबंधन के लिए परफेक्ट स्टेप बाय स्टेप आसान और झटपट रेसिपी, How to make Malai Ghevar using Atta, Crispy and Delicious Ghevar Recipe for festivals.

#rakhispecial #ghevar #mithai #sweets 

Ingredients for Atta Ghevar
घी - Ghee - 5 tbsp (60 grams)
दूध - Milk - 1/2 cup
गेहूं का आटा - Wheat flour - 2 cup (250 grams)
चीनी - Sugar - 1 cup (225 grams)
इलाइची - Cardamom - 2-3 no, crushed
रबड़ी - Rabri
बादाम कतरन - Almond flakes
पिस्ता कतरन - Pistachio Flakes
केसर - Saffron - 3-4 strands

तेल और घी तलने के लिये
Oil & Ghee for frying

snippet.title: Muttai Mittai Recipe in Tamil | Egg Sweet Recipe in Tamil
snippet.description:
In this video we will see how to make muttai mittai recipe in tamil. This egg sweet is a very popular sweet recipe which can be made with a handful of ingredients. The original recipe for Syed Muttai mittai uses Khoya but if Khoya is not available we can stir and evaporate 1 litre of milk to make about 200g of khoya. This egg sweet has a melt in mouth soft texture and smooth finish to it and is definitely a wonderful recipe to make during the holidays.
#eggsweet #muttaimittai

Friends, please do try this egg sweet recipe at home and share it with your friends and family. Also, please do share your feedback about the recipe in the comments below. All the best and happy cooking!

200g unsweetened Khoya (or 1 liter full fat milk to make khoya)
6 Eggs
1/4 cup Ghee (50g)
1/2 tsp fresh Cardamom powder
1 cup Sugar (200g)
Bake at 160C / 320F for 35-40 min
